life or death decisions on your own,

554
00:41:51,133 --> 00:41:53,219
the same could always happen again.

555
00:41:54,220 --> 00:41:55,804
Just like three years ago.

556
00:41:58,974 --> 00:42:00,351
So what then?

557
00:42:01,936 --> 00:42:04,480
If you're so worried about
what happened three years ago,

558
00:42:04,563 --> 00:42:06,357
you should've prevented my appointment.

559
00:42:06,774 --> 00:42:09,860
Or summon me
to the ethics commission right now.

560
00:42:10,027 --> 00:42:11,695
Of course, there's no reason

561
00:42:11,987 --> 00:42:14,073
for me to go that far to stay here.

562
00:42:14,615 --> 00:42:15,449
Is there?

563
00:42:27,461 --> 00:42:30,047
