I'll come with you.

564
00:42:30,214 --> 00:42:31,215
Stay out of it.

565
00:42:33,926 --> 00:42:37,096
-Don't come with me. Didn't you hear?
-The patient refused treatment.

566
00:42:37,179 --> 00:42:38,681
If something happens when you--

567
00:42:38,764 --> 00:42:41,809
So stay out of it
before you get into trouble too.

568
00:42:49,858 --> 00:42:51,902
Do you want to learn from me?

569
00:42:53,737 --> 00:42:54,738
Don't learn this.

