A doctor here killed a patient.

605
00:44:18,947 --> 00:44:21,450
I think it's about his brain, not his eye.

606
00:44:21,533 --> 00:44:24,286
He could have MS
or ophthalmoneuromyelitis.

607
00:44:24,370 --> 00:44:26,038
You must take a brain MRI to check.

608
00:44:26,121 --> 00:44:28,332
Do you think we didn't do anything?

609
00:44:28,874 --> 00:44:31,293
We persuaded him to get a brain MRI.

610
00:44:31,377 --> 00:44:33,629
-What were the results?
-We just got it back.

611
00:44:33,712 --> 00:44:34,963
There are no lesions.

612
00:44:37,841 --> 00:44:40,594
If you're satisfied now,
go see the patient.

613
00:44:41,637 --> 00:44:44,098
-Can I see him?
-He wants to see you.

614
00:44:44,181 --> 00:44:46,392
-He has something to tell you.
-Me?

615
00:44:46,475 --> 00:44:47,559
Yes.

616
00:45:05,786 --> 00:45:07,287
You wanted to see me?

617
00:45:07,704 --> 00:45:09,665
-Say no! Say no!
-Say no! Say no!

618
